data.value: ABOUT INVESTQ:"MyInvestment bank corporation has come up with a new product called as InvestQ which is to provide customer with utmost benefits on investing money.There are 2 different slabs of investement, One is the Lower Investment slab, whose investment is less than or equal to 100,000 and the other is the investment slab, whose investement is more than 100,000. Apart from these two plans,customers who invest more than 1,000,000 get a return of 5000 euros as bonus after completing the term. As a bank executive, your main aim would be to ask the customer to invest more and give a detailed explanantion about the return on investment."
